{
  "stem": "8947.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then when night came, you know, they didn't check us, because they put us in another-- other-- another barracks, other camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was a chaos and transportation problems.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, at night, you know, I pulled out my little jars.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had to eat those two jars, because I couldn't risk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I thought, how I am going to take these out in the morning without being checked, you know, the jars.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you put it in the mattress, they check your mattress every day, to see if you have paper or pencil.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was gravely punished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And through the night, I-- in the-- I gorged myself with those two things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you know, in the morning, my whole sore throat-- everything was gone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I could never understand, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was a miracle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Those two little jars, you know, lasted for the night and made me hap-- made me healthy in the morning.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we stayed there through winter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was a terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, by the end of winter-- but at least, the one thing, you were working on the streets.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And if you had a bad guard, he didn't let you do anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But if you had a Wehrmacht, one of the Wehrmacht-- very few, maybe two that I can count-- maybe they let you raid the garbage can if you wanted it, you know?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, it was-- it was a-- maybe you can get some scraps of food from somewhere, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But you had to be careful, because it depended what guard you had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And were heavy labor-- we had to lift heavy stones, heavy pipes, bricks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And one thing sticks out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "At one point, there was a heavy thing we had to carry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we are women.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
